Panoramix mixnet server and client
==================================

Installation
------------

In a virtualenv, run:

  pip install -r requirements.txt
  python setup.py install

This packages includes three cryptographic backends: 'gpg', 'zeus', and
'sphinxmix'. In order to use them, you must install the respective
dependencies with:

  pip install panoramix[zeus]
  pip install panoramix[sphinxmix]
  pip install panoramix[gpg]


Demo
----

For a demonstration of Panoramix workflow, see demo/README.


